        "username": "hiran",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/h/53a042/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2025-05-07T17:49:04.791Z",
        "cooked": "<p>The link to join groups is very long. It would be better if you made it shorter, like on WhatsApp. Long links cause concerns for users when they post them on WhatsApp and other apps. Editing the link and previewing the group name without logging in helps you join groups faster than on other apps. I hope you make this change if you want to advance this app and keep up with other apps. When posting a Signal group link on other apps, the preview doesn’t show the group name, but rather a preview of the login process. This poses concerns for users, especially those who are new to the app. Thank you very much.</p>",
