        "created_at": "2025-05-10T20:10:21.262Z",
        "cooked": "<p>again, the server can’t generate a preview for you as it’ll require it to know info about the group. the client could possibly generate them, but that will require it parsing the code, which i doubt any client other than Signal will ever try. and Signal does already generate group link previews. so without convincing other clients to parse the fragment, i don’t think there’s much more to do.</p>",
